{{vgname|忍者蛙|ja=バトルトード|en=Battletoads}}是一款由[[Rare|Rare]]公司制作、[[Tradewest|Tradewest]]发行的[[动作游戏|动作游戏]]。<ref name="mobygames">[http://www.mobygames.com/game/battletoads ''battletoads''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/battletoads |date=20210117141447 }} game overview at [[MobyGames|MobyGames]]</ref>本游戏是忍者蛙系列的第一作。本游戏于1991年6月1日在北美地区NES发行，于同年12月20日在日本地区[[紅白機|FC游戏机]]发行。<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamefaqs.com/nes/587125-battletoads/data| title = Release information| publisher = [[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]| date = | accessdate = 2015-07-24| archive-date = 2017-01-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170116200206/http://www.gamefaqs.com/nes/587125-battletoads/data| dead-url = no}}</ref>游戏后移植至其他多个平台，包括[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive]]、[[Amiga|Amiga]]、[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]和[[Game_Gear|Game Gear]]。在游戏中，两个星际变种战士忍者蛙Rash和Zitz前往黑暗女王的星球，去完成营救被拐走的Pimple和Angelica公主并击败黑暗女王的任务。

本游戏是根据[[忍者神龟|忍者神龟]]的火热而推出。游戏为横向卷轴，内容为忍者蛙的竞速、攀爬和格斗。

本游戏收到多个正面评价。[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]给与Mega Drive版本73%的分数。<ref name="GR">{{cite web|title=Battletoads aggregate score (Mega Drive)|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/genesis/586053-battletoads/index.html|publisher=GameRankings|accessdate=13 September 2015|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209015000/https://www.gamerankings.com/genesis/586053-battletoads/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

忍者蛙的游戏难度被认为极度困难。<ref>{{cite web|first=Levi|last=Buchanan|url=http://retro.ign.com/articles/944/944561p1.html|title=Battletoads Retrospective|publisher=IGN|date=13 January 2009|accessdate=21 February 2009|archive-date=2012-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819021625/http://retro.ign.com/articles/944/944561p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=O'Brien |first=Jack |url=http://www.cracked.com/blog/7-dick-moves-everyone-pulled-in-classic-video-games/ |title=7 Dick Moves Everyone Pulled in Classic Video Games |publisher=Cracked.com |date= |accessdate=20 December 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031344/https://www.cracked.com/blog/7-dick-moves-everyone-pulled-in-classic-video-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

